": [{"author": "athena.smith.146", "author_id": "6890746243", "id": "18079412660526450", "text": "Thank you. I have shutdown, to a certain extent. I'm not sure I can come back. But I'm grateful you and so many others are willing and able to fight. Thank you.", "timestamp": 1775149077}, {"author": "angel.7215", "author_id": "8210934111", "id": "18124699060606640", "text": "I agree!  Thank you", "timestamp": 1775061987}, {"author": "peregrineeam", "author_id": "8248921987", "id": "18117140737630797", "text": "Le problème, c'est encore l'hégémonie des Américains. Ces barbares. Les pires sur cette terre. Ils ont fondé leur Nation sur le Crime contre L'Humanité et n'ont jamais cessé de perpétrer des crimes contre l'humanité. Autrefois les Indiens, les Indochinois, les Africains, etc. aujourd'hui les Enfants. Ils sont assoiffés de conquête et de sang, et leur système est basé sur le chantage et les abus de pouvoir.", "timestamp": 1775055250}, {"author": "ms._kacz", "author_id": "3246205792", "id": "18160285759440087", "text": "True", "timestamp": 1775053019}, {"author": "bellabellissimaboutiquebakery", "author_id": "64482740714", "id": "18098998364074725", "text": "Thank you for this. 🫶🏻", "timestamp": 1775018284}, {"author": "keebs_elf5", "author_id": "7309401514", "id": "18576320467013133", "text": "Having felt numb since trump was elected again, I think reading the deeper horrors myself would scar my soul beyond repair. Just learning what I have through what others post about the file content has lit a flame of rage that I carry, but don’t know how to control yet. I have a young son, so until I know how to be the most effective and constructive with my rage, I will be pouring all of my energy into teaching my own child about humanity, compassion, and empathy. There will come a day, not soon enough, when those of us walking around with that flame of rage will know what needs to be done.", "timestamp": 1774933726}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/629278268_1582063986376838_142495275847754030_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4LmRlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=102&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gEatqW4vzMUl7eMhNtePih7758JVXX993qM0rdq2Xehs0etWKn6yuRWNpG7Ra-N8t0&_nc_ohc=SiGl7xHU_2sQ7kNvwE3IpJ6&_nc_gid=J1FNq1mN53xuKZyjN5osvg&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af0oIvBbI7BZ0S_Q6D9uv1bCdaouX7DRyrqrITGnWcbQoQ&oe=69D4D2D1&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 640, "height": 1136, "id": "0", "resolution": "640x1136"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/629278268_1582063986376838_142495275847754030_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4LmRlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=102&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gEatqW4vzMUl7eMhNtePih7758JVXX993qM0rdq2Xehs0etWKn6yuRWNpG7Ra-N8t0&_nc_ohc=SiGl7xHU_2sQ7kNvwE3IpJ6&_nc_gid=J1FNq1mN53xuKZyjN5osvg&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af0oIvBbI7BZ0S_Q6D9uv1bCdaouX7DRyrqrITGnWcbQoQ&oe=69D4D2D1&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 750, "height": 1331, "id": "1", "resolution": "750x1331"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/629278268_1582063986376838_142495275847754030_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4LmRlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=102&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gEatqW4vzMUl7eMhNtePih7758JVXX993qM0rdq2Xehs0etWKn6yuRWNpG7Ra-N8t0&_nc_ohc=SiGl7xHU_2sQ7kNvwE3IpJ6&_nc_gid=J1FNq1mN53xuKZyjN5osvg&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af0oIvBbI7BZ0S_Q6D9uv1bCdaouX7DRyrqrITGnWcbQoQ&oe=69D4D2D1&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 1080, "height": 1917, "id": "2", "resolution": "1080x1917"}], "http_headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/143.0.0.0 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9